title: Kevin Owens launches surprise attack on Chris Jericho in Germany
text:
Feb 25, 2017 at 5:55p ET 0Shares 
Looks like Chris Jericho and Kevin Owens are best friends no more. 
The Festival of Friendship and the subsequent attack by the WWE Universal champion ended their mutual comradeship. 
This is what happened a couple weeks ago on Raw when Owens presented Jericho with his own version of “The List.” 
Jericho was still recovering from his injuries last week on Raw, but he made a surprise appearance on Saturday at the company’s show in Regensburg, Germany. 
WWE posted a video of Owens attacking and beating down Jericho, who was on crutches.
